item.title: Grumpy, Complaining, Tantrumy Kids from Ages 2-22?
item.description: Do you have a child who can be grumpy, throws tantrums, complains about everything that’s wrong, controls the emotional tide of your home, whose mood does determine your mood? What if your child wakes up miserable and makes everyone else miserable? Kirk gives you action steps and scripts in this powerful podcast with lots of insight into strong-willed kids…from toddler through teen years! Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/CELBL1853551588
